rows.label: tlk47300163_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Poor old Liberalitas doesn't have nearly
as much soil and greenery as other
Divine Beasts.

rows.label: tlk47300163_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It's hard to come by veg if you don't
grow some yourself.

rows.label: tlk47300163_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I remember you used to help out in the
field back when you were small, Rex.
You were a good little tyke...

rows.label: tlk47300163_01_msg0103
rows.name:
I bet Rex hasn't told you all how he
used to help out in the fields when he
was little. A good little tyke, he was!
